.claude/
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
.cursor/
.cursorrules
.github/copilot-instructions.md
docs/NEXT_SESSION_PLAN.md

# Runtime config/data generated on a live server
/config/
/run*/config/
**/profiles/
whitelist.json

